    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit delivers linear power through its six individual throttle bodies and is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Recent preventive maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural rigidity under high-torque loads. The factory M-Variable Differential Lock remains tight, providing exceptional corner-exit traction. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains robust with consistent compression across all cylinders. A purist-spec driver's car ready for the apex.",
