      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a refined driving experience and exceptional value. The exterior presents beautifully with a high-gloss finish, showing only the minor, expected road wear of a well-loved car. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and smoke-free; the upholstery is supple, the carpets are pristine, and every electronic feature\u2014from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in top form, having recently passed a comprehensive multi-point inspection with a fresh oil change and fluid top-off. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the engine provides smooth, responsive power. Accompanied by a complete set of service records and tires with plenty of tread remaining, this car is turn-key ready for its next owner.",
